title: OSOM Finance. The easiest way to grow your crypto

creator: Polybius Tech OÜ
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to OSOM Finance, your EU-based crypto partner and creator of the Crypto Autopilot. Our AI-powered algorithm will take care of your crypto holdings (or create a crypto portfolio from scratch, if you don’t have one yet) in one easy-to-use app. Whether you are a newbie or a crypto veteran, we have you covered!

Our app allows you to invest in over 60 carefully selected coins with ease and confidence. AI technology does all the hard work behind the scenes, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year, so you don't have to. Without any input from you, our Autopilot algorithm continuously optimises your portfolio of coins to achieve the best return on your investment.

Unlike the traditional financial markets that do actually close, crypto markets never stop trading so it's really a full time job to stay on top of things. Let's not forget that the world of coins is also way more volatile! Let our Crypto Autopilot keep an eye on your crypto holdings leaving you free to enjoy life.

Why our 6,000+ users love Crypto Autopilot?

Secure and regulated – We are an authorised virtual asset wallet and exchange service provider with the Estonian Financial Intelligence Unit.

Completely hands-off – No need to manage, trade, or read up on daily finance & crypto news. Our committee keeps an eye on the market to select the best projects and our algorithm adapts the portfolio strategy for you.

We hate hidden fees – No entry fees. No exit fees. No management fees. Only a 10% commission on the monthly BTC profit you earn. If there are no gains you pay no management fee, it’s that simple. The only fees are if you don’t have Bitcoin and start with fiat. We have a low 5% payment processing fee on card transactions and SEPA deposits are free. Conversion to BTC is 1.5%. Smart diversification - Our algorithm finds growth opportunities in real-time in the crypto market and makes trades that are optimised to continually increase the value of your portfolio.

Full flexibility – Start for free! With just a few easy steps, you’ll be ready to go. You can add or withdraw funds anytime you like.

Minimal drawdowns – OSOM Crypto Autopilot was built to minimise drawdowns and perform better than market indexes, especially in a bear market. In case you're not familiar with the term, drawdowns are the periods of time when the value of your portfolio drops and then recovers again. Our algorithm is specifically designed to minimise the investment risk. This being crypto, it’s still not all “chill”, though.

How does Crypto Autopilot work?

Every day, our committee composed of experts from Investsuite and OSOM assesses the most promising crypto assets and defines the Autopilot’s investment universe.

Based on this pre-selected list of over 60 different crypto assets, our algorithm will allocate positions. No single position is allowed to represent more than 40% of the portfolio. This allocation aims to improve the risk-adjusted returns, meaning less risks for a given return.

The assets are selected according to quality, market cap, as well as trading volume. Our trading universe does not include dubious projects, stablecoins, synthetics or tokenised assets of gold or real estate. We tap into the potential of genuine crypto projects and nothing else.

title: OSOM Finance. The easiest way to grow your crypto

creator: Polybius Tech OÜ
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to OSOM Finance, your EU-based crypto partner and creator of the Crypto Autopilot. Our AI-powered algorithm will take care of your crypto holdings (or create a crypto portfolio from scratch, if you don’t have one yet) in one easy-to-use app. Whether you are a newbie or a crypto veteran, we have you covered!

Our app allows you to invest in over 60 carefully selected coins with ease and confidence. AI technology does all the hard work behind the scenes, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year, so you don't have to. Without any input from you, our Autopilot algorithm continuously optimises your portfolio of coins to achieve the best return on your investment.

Unlike the traditional financial markets that do actually close, crypto markets never stop trading so it's really a full time job to stay on top of things. Let's not forget that the world of coins is also way more volatile! Let our Crypto Autopilot keep an eye on your crypto holdings leaving you free to enjoy life.

Why our 6,000+ users love Crypto Autopilot?

Secure and regulated – We are an authorised virtual asset wallet and exchange service provider with the Estonian Financial Intelligence Unit.

Completely hands-off – No need to manage, trade, or read up on daily finance & crypto news. Our committee keeps an eye on the market to select the best projects and our algorithm adapts the portfolio strategy for you.

We hate hidden fees – No entry fees. No exit fees. No management fees. Only a 10% commission on the monthly BTC profit you earn. If there are no gains you pay no management fee, it’s that simple. The only fees are if you don’t have Bitcoin and start with fiat. We have a low 5% payment processing fee on card transactions and SEPA deposits are free. Conversion to BTC is 1.5%. Smart diversification - Our algorithm finds growth opportunities in real-time in the crypto market and makes trades that are optimised to continually increase the value of your portfolio.

Full flexibility – Start for free! With just a few easy steps, you’ll be ready to go. You can add or withdraw funds anytime you like.

Minimal drawdowns – OSOM Crypto Autopilot was built to minimise drawdowns and perform better than market indexes, especially in a bear market. In case you're not familiar with the term, drawdowns are the periods of time when the value of your portfolio drops and then recovers again. Our algorithm is specifically designed to minimise the investment risk. This being crypto, it’s still not all “chill”, though.

How does Crypto Autopilot work?

Every day, our committee composed of experts from Investsuite and OSOM assesses the most promising crypto assets and defines the Autopilot’s investment universe.

Based on this pre-selected list of over 60 different crypto assets, our algorithm will allocate positions. No single position is allowed to represent more than 40% of the portfolio. This allocation aims to improve the risk-adjusted returns, meaning less risks for a given return.

The assets are selected according to quality, market cap, as well as trading volume. Our trading universe does not include dubious projects, stablecoins, synthetics or tokenised assets of gold or real estate. We tap into the potential of genuine crypto projects and nothing else.
descriptionShort: Buy, sell, grow and track cryptocurrencies

title: OSOM Finance. The easiest way to grow your crypto

creator: Polybius Tech OÜ
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to OSOM Finance, your EU-based crypto partner and creator of the Crypto Autopilot, DeFi Earn and Bitcoin Gift. Three highly innovative yet easy to use products taking advantage of the massive opportunities in the world of crypto today and best of all, you don’t need to know a thing about tech, crypto or investing.

Crypto Autopilot – Why risk putting all your eggs in one basket? Put your funds on autopilot instead! Our Crypto Autopilot uses cutting edge artificial intelligence technology to turn your deposited funds into a managed crypto portfolio that continually responds to market fluctuations 24/7 365 days a year. With Crypto Autopilot your funds are strategically spread across a carefully chosen portfolio of crypto assets, minimising investment risk and improving performance opportunities for you.

DeFi Earn – A great way to earn a healthy passive income, and by passive, we really do mean, totally hands-off and passive. One of the most exciting areas in crypto right now is Decentralised Finance or DeFi for short. It is a highly complex area where deep knowledge is highly advantageous. Luckily you don’t need to know a thing about crypto or DeFi and with interest rates being so historically low, DeFi Earn offers you a way to earn 6-8% passive income on your assets without you needing to do a thing.

Bitcoin Gift – We know it’s always a challenge coming up with useful and thoughtful gift ideas. While cash and vouchers are practical, they can be somewhat boring and impersonal. Why not give the gift of Bitcoin using OSOM Gift, it’s super easy and an ideal way to either top up the lucky recipient’s personal Bitcoin holdings or get someone started on their very own crypto journey!

Crypto Autopilot
Our AI-powered algorithm will take care of your crypto holdings (or create a crypto portfolio from scratch, if you don’t have one yet) in one easy-to-use app. Whether you are a newbie or a crypto veteran, we have you covered!
Our app allows you to invest in a universe of over 60 carefully selected coins with ease and confidence.

Why do our 6,000+ users love Crypto Autopilot?
- secure and regulated
- completely hands-off
- no hidden fees
- smart diversification
- you can add or withdraw funds anytime you like
- ability to perform better than market indexes

How does Crypto Autopilot work?
Based on this pre-selected list of over 60 different crypto assets, our algorithm will allocate positions. This allocation aims to improve the risk-adjusted returns, meaning less risks for a given return. The assets are selected according to quality, market cap, as well as trading volume.


DeFi Earn
With DeFi Earn we take care of the difficult decisions and provide you with an easy way to earn a passive income from crypto. With interest rates being so low DeFi Earn provides the perfect opportunity to potentially earn 6 – 8% per year from crypto stablecoins.

What is DeFi earn? DeFi earn is an aggregator of centralised as well as DeFi lending platforms. What we do is convert your EUR deposit into what are known as stablecoins and allocate them across several platforms that allow you to earn interest. With DeFi earn we seek out the most reputable and profitable platforms to deposit the stablecoins. It’s easy, you simply deposit your funds and leave the rest to us.

Gift
Why is Bitcoin a great gift idea? There will only ever be 21 million Bitcoin. This scarcity amongst other things makes bitcoin valuable, just as is the case with gold and oil. Bitcoin is a truly global peer to peer digital currency, this means that a Bitcoin holder can send or receive payments from anyone on the network around the world without requiring approval from any external source or authority.
It’s super easy to gift Bitcoin with OSOM. Start by downloading our app, next you sign up. We will verify your identity and then you can deposit your EUR. Next, choose the amount of Bitcoin (BTC) you would like to gift and share the link with the lucky person.

Three highly innovative yet easy to use products taking advantage of the massive opportunities in the world of crypto today and best of all, you don’t need to know a thing about tech, crypto or investing.

Crypto Autopilot – Why risk putting all your eggs in one basket? Put your funds on autopilot instead! Our Crypto Autopilot uses cutting edge artificial intelligence technology to turn your deposited funds into a managed crypto portfolio that continually responds to market fluctuations 24/7 365 days a year. With Crypto Autopilot your funds are strategically spread across a carefully chosen portfolio of crypto assets, minimising investment risk and improving performance opportunities for you.

DeFi Earn – A great way to earn a healthy passive income, and by passive, we really do mean, totally hands-off and passive. One of the most exciting areas in crypto right now is Decentralised Finance or DeFi for short. It is a highly complex area where deep knowledge is highly advantageous. Luckily you don’t need to know a thing about crypto or DeFi and with interest rates being so historically low, DeFi Earn offers you a way to earn 6-8% passive income on your assets without you needing to do a thing.

Bitcoin Gift – We know it’s always a challenge coming up with useful and thoughtful gift ideas. While cash and vouchers are practical, they can be somewhat boring and impersonal. Why not give the gift of Bitcoin using OSOM Gift, it’s super easy and an ideal way to either top up the lucky recipient’s personal Bitcoin holdings or get someone started on their very own crypto journey!

Crypto Autopilot
Our AI-powered algorithm will take care of your crypto holdings (or create a crypto portfolio from scratch, if you don’t have one yet) in one easy-to-use app. Whether you are a newbie or a crypto veteran, we have you covered!
Our app allows you to invest in a universe of over 60 carefully selected coins with ease and confidence.

Why do our 6,000+ users love Crypto Autopilot?
- secure and regulated
- completely hands-off
- no hidden fees
- smart diversification
- you can add or withdraw funds anytime you like
- ability to perform better than market indexes

How does Crypto Autopilot work?
Based on this pre-selected list of over 60 different crypto assets, our algorithm will allocate positions. This allocation aims to improve the risk-adjusted returns, meaning less risks for a given return. The assets are selected according to quality, market cap, as well as trading volume.


DeFi Earn
With DeFi Earn we take care of the difficult decisions and provide you with an easy way to earn a passive income from crypto. With interest rates being so low DeFi Earn provides the perfect opportunity to potentially earn 6 – 8% per year from crypto stablecoins.

What is DeFi earn? DeFi earn is an aggregator of centralised as well as DeFi lending platforms. What we do is convert your EUR deposit into what are known as stablecoins and allocate them across several platforms that allow you to earn interest. With DeFi earn we seek out the most reputable and profitable platforms to deposit the stablecoins. It’s easy, you simply deposit your funds and leave the rest to us.

Gift
Why is Bitcoin a great gift idea? There will only ever be 21 million Bitcoin. This scarcity amongst other things makes bitcoin valuable, just as is the case with gold and oil. Bitcoin is a truly global peer to peer digital currency, this means that a Bitcoin holder can send or receive payments from anyone on the network around the world without requiring approval from any external source or authority.
It’s super easy to gift Bitcoin with OSOM. Start by downloading our app, next you sign up. We will verify your identity and then you can deposit your EUR. Next, choose the amount of Bitcoin (BTC) you would like to gift and share the link with the lucky person.
